  "content": {
    "prompt": "<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows blocks X and Y placed in contact next to each other. Block Y is larger than block X.\" src=\"/images/1b36be0a1ef3ed6de3d2a5f2d56c5f6d.svg\"></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Two blocks, <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"X\"><math alttext=\"X\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mtext>X</mtext></mstyle></math></span></span> and <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"Y\"><math alttext=\"Y\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mtext>Y</mtext></mstyle></math></span></span>, are at the same temperature when they are put into thermal contact, as shown. Block <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"X\"><math alttext=\"X\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mtext>X</mtext></mstyle></math></span></span> has mass <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"m\"><math alttext=\"m\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mi>m</mi></mstyle></math></span></span> and volume <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"V\"><math alttext=\"V\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mi>V</mi></mstyle></math></span></span>. Block <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"Y\"><math alttext=\"Y\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mtext>Y</mtext></mstyle></math></span></span> has mass <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"m over 2\"><math alttext=\"m over 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mfrac><mi>m</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mstyle></math></span></span> and a volume of <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2 V\"><math alttext=\"2 V\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mn>2</mn><mi>V</mi></mstyle></math></spa